item.description:
Hi! All! My friend's band is playing at "Killarney's" in Nashua this coming Sat. The band starts at 9:00PM so I thought if people wanted to meet there for 7:00PM to get seats and have something to eat that would be fun! I know there are a lot of fun members out there who love to dance so why not!

Pam Taber

Like any bar there may be a cover charge after 9PM. They play a lot of Bonnie Raitt and songs from the 60's, 70's and 80's. Look them up on Facebook to find out more. I went to a event back in December and the dance floor was hopping!

group.name: Meeting & Greeting in So. NH & the Merrimack Valley :)

item.name: Dancing to " Casual 6" at Killarney' in Nashua
